00:45:04,208 --> 00:45:08,333
<i>♪ If I stay with you</i>
<i>If I'm choosing wrong ♪</i>

677
00:45:08,416 --> 00:45:10,666
<i>♪ I don't care at all ♪</i>

678
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:16,541
<i>♪ If I'm losing now</i>
<i>But I'm winning late ♪</i>

679
